text: James Ammon Ellisor (born March 9, 1990) is a professional basketball player who plays for Sporting CP. Before going to Portugal, James played for Glendale CC Gauchos and Bemidji State Beavers. ==Honours== Oliveirense * Portuguese League: 2017-18, 2018-19 * Portuguese League Cup: 2018-19 * Portuguese Supercup: 2018 ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:American men's basketball players Category:Sporting CP basketball players Category:Small forwards
